::DrillBit::

"Yeah, we have CR facilities." He picked up Dollen, from the legs.
"Help me carry him." He says.

::K-9::

He looked at the bot.
"I am K-9. I have come from Cybertron, to help the Maximals. I am here
to join your faction." He said, walking into the ship.
